/**
 * Integration test template with Kafka TestContainer.
 *
 * Usage:
 * 1. Replace ${producerName} and ${consumerName} with your classes
 * 2. Replace ${messageName} with your message class
 * 3. Replace ${topicName} with your Kafka topic
 * 4. Add test methods for producer/consumer scenarios
 *
 * Requirements:
 * - Docker must be running
 * - testImplementation "org.testcontainers:kafka"
 * - testImplementation "ru.tinkoff.kora:kafka"
